title: One Man's Justice a.k.a. One Tough Bastard (1995) DVDRip
description:
An Army drill sergeant scours the streets of Venice, California for the killers of his wife and daughter. In his search for vengeance he comes across a streetwise 10-year-old who may be able to help him in his quest. Starring Brian Bosworth.
